===Etymology===
Named for the city of ''[[w:Pergamon|Pergamon]]'', where it was invented.

===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}

# A material, made from the [[skin]] of a [[calf]], [[sheep]], or [[goat]], used like [[paper]] for writing.
# A [[diploma]].

